## Decision Log

Here's every non-obvious choice and which project rule drove it:

| Decision | Rule |
|---|---|
| `useQuery` instead of `useState` + `useEffect` | **[f001]** TanStack Query owns all server state |
| No Redux `createSlice` / `dispatch` | **[f002]** Redux was retired in ADR-007 |
| `role="status"` + `aria-label` on skeleton; `role="alert"` on error; `scope="col"` on `<th>` | **[f004]** All interactive/informational elements need accessible labels |
| Zero custom CSS; all layout via Tailwind classes | **[f005]** Tailwind-only styling policy |
| `<Image>` from `next/image` with explicit `width`/`height` | **[f008]** Raw `<img>` is banned for production assets |
| `Error` typed explicitly in `useQuery<Order[], Error>` | **[f003]** No `any`; typed generics instead |
| Fetcher function defined outside the component | Cache sharing — if two components mount simultaneously, TanStack Query deduplicates the network request automatically |
